reviewText: This is a promotional video for Isagenix. It contains segments from several of Gilad's other workout videos; specifically "New Beginners Weight Loss & Toning Program", "Sculpt & Tone Workout", and "45/45 Split Routine Workout". There is no unique material on this Isagenix one.
Other than the dated music (Techno/disco) which I don't mind, this is a good workout.  It is the most fun if you have a partner, but can be done alone as well.
